Parmesan Roasted Broccoli

1. Preheat oven to 200 degrees celcius. 2. Cut and wash broccoli. 3. Crush garlic. 3. Add all ingredients to ziplock back and shake to coat broccoli well. 4. Evenly spread broccoli on baking sheet and put in the oven for 15-20 minutes

Ingredients

Serving

600 Gram Broccoli

20 Gram Parmesan cheese

2 Piece Garlic

20 Gram Bread crumbs

30 Milliliters Olive oil

Preparation

none
